tedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T04:33:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫手吸乾港豬血同儲備進貢支共狗，係外籍大中華賣港賊本能常識吧！！！</span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"291ff169e76f97d6b9600bc826197fbdbf949e80","tid":193993,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T04:38:29.000Z","msg":"李嘉誠狂賣支那資產<br />\n<br />\n支那資產有入無出<br />\n<br />\n823走去買支那資產?<br />\n<br />\n係都去新加坡買啦"},{"pid":"1b2224a313df3cf72a9bce092020ba63ec2e8bc0","tid":193993,"uid":16414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T04:44:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>家下支那D商場有撚人行咩? 間間都靜過圖書館 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根本無咩人鐘意行商場, 大陸仲有街行搵鬼去行商場.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個商場都可以嘅<br />\n夜晚好多街坊上去行 涼冷氣<br />\n同埋間百佳都幾好生意<br />\n最近又多左食店, <br />\n反而係李嘉誠時期仲頹"}]}